DSET ^les_02-05.atm
OPTIONS BIG_ENDIAN
OPTIONS template
TITLE les_02-05.atm
UNDEF 1.0e+37
XDEF        25 LINEAR 1 1
YDEF         1 LINEAR 1 1
ZDEF        16 LINEAR 1 1
TDEF       1 LINEAR 00:00Z00JAN0001 1YR
VARS    5
tmpa3d      16 99 Temperature perturbation (K)
absg3d      16 99 Absorption coefficient perturbation (/m)
extp3d      16 99 Extinction coefficient (/m)
omgp3d      16 99 Single scattering albedo
apfp3d      16 99 Phase function specification parameter
ENDVARS
